<h2>Parsing your <a href="http://humanstxt.org/">humans.txt</a> into JSON</h2>

<div class="content">
  <h3>GET /:host?use_ssl=true</h3>

  <dl>
    <dt>host</dt>
    <dd>A host (domain) with a humans.txt</dd>
    <dt>
      use_ssl
      <em>(Optional)</em>
    </dt>
    <dd>Set to <b>true</b> if your domain requires HTTPS</dd>
  </dl>
</div>

<div class="examples">
  <h4>Examples</h4>
  <pre>curl https://humans.herokuapp.com/c7.se | json -i</pre>
  <pre>curl https://humans.herokuapp.com/humanstxt.org | json -i</pre>
  <pre>curl https://humans.herokuapp.com/cheddarapp.com?use_ssl=true | json -i</pre>
</div>
